        ],
        [
          "Compass.c",
          "3.2.1.14.13 Compass Display",
          "IPC 通过罗盘向乘客显示车辆方向 from COM Compass_Run FU21_Action12P->CompassRecalibrate_ActionHandler 罗盘重新标定 FU21_Action13P->CompassSetZone_ActionHandler 罗盘区域设定 FU21_Action53P->CompassAreaSlctn_ActionHandler 罗盘区域选择 ![](https://img4.cache.netease.com/photo/0008/2014-05-30/300x225_9TG4D8V629GL0008.jpg)"
